Package: FluentVCF
Type: Package
Title: Processes VariantCallFormat file
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mirco", "Macchi", email = "mirco.macchi@live.it",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Return,summarizes and plots information regarding each mutation in VCF file.
        The mutation type is UP[REF>ALT]DOWN. 
        where REF>ALT is the single nucleotide variant from REF base to ALT. 
        e.g., C>T.
Imports: 
    GenomicRanges,
